Package: mema
Version: 0.0.1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Eugen Lupricht <mema@lupricht.net>
Depends: curl, bash, git, jq, tar, xz-utils, ca-certificates, fzf
Recommends: unzip
Description: The Minimalist Meta-Manager
 Who needs an OS when you have apt and sh?
 Mema is a lightweight POSIX-sh framework to manage binaries 
 and completions in /opt and /etc without the bloat.
